 fields, in order to establish the\nmagnetic correction to the instability window.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2013 18:12:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2013 04:21:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-11-27"}
