\\sim 2.0$,\nthe $g-$band magnitude becomes smaller by $1.5$\\,mag, the $g-r$ color becomes\nbluer by $1.0$\\,mag, and the $u-g$ color becomes redder by $1.0$\\,mag when\nbinary interactions are included.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Aug 2013 04:16:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-20"}
